{"tid":1954243,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"為出門不惜秀下限！ 英國人「扮樹木」、「扮垃圾」","createTime":"2020-04-01T16:27:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T07:17:50.000Z","uid":226548,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"0aef749775ff6248095e32acfde45e097a0c10fe","tid":1954243,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T16:27:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/03/31/99/7672327.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=930&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=465\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F03%2F31%2F99%2F7672327.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D930%26exp%3D3600%26w%3D465&h=f8152514&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/03/31/99/7672330.jpg&amp;s=Y&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=233&amp;sh=420&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=400\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F03%2F31%2F99%2F7672330.jpg%26s%3DY%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D233%26sh%3D420%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26w%3D400&h=f891a93a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情全球延燒，英國從一開始的「佛系防疫」，到後來宣布實施3週禁足令，可說是政策大轉彎。許多被「悶壞」的英國人開始想辦法溜出門透氣，就<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有人套上黑色大垃圾袋</span></strong>，讓自己看起來像堆放在路邊的垃圾；<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">也有人將自己打扮成綠色灌木叢</span></strong>，隱身在路邊樹林裡，等路上沒車流經過時再跑來跑去。<br />\n<br />\n日前有網友在抖音（TikTok）放上一段影片，只見空無一人的街道上，原本路邊種植高矮不一的樹叢，竟有一棵動了起來。那棵「灌木叢」從街邊小路跑到馬路口蹲下，確認四下無人，再狂奔過馬路，到對街的綠色草坪上蹲下，遠看宛如一棵種在路邊的綠樹。偶爾發現汽車駛過，「灌木叢」會先暫時停下來，或者在柏油馬路上連滾帶爬，讓錄下這段影片的居民笑道「鄰居已經將事情做到極致了！」"},{"pid":"e0e85253c5aa27f5e780a5a5e4530fcb772fe9b8","tid":1954243,"uid":226548,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T16:29:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/03/31/99/7672331.jpg&amp;s=Y&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=262&amp;sh=401&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=400\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F03%2F31%2F99%2F7672331.jpg%26s%3DY%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D262%26sh%3D401%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26w%3D400&h=912adf6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同樣在英國的另一個社區，市容規劃沒什麼綠樹，就有兩個人穿上黑色垃圾袋，在路上奔跑。當他們蹲在路邊時，乍看之下跟被丟棄的臭垃圾沒兩樣。為了出門無所不用其極。英國23日進入為期三周的「全境封鎖」的日常暫停狀態，除了民生必需與特定行業外，其餘全停工停班；非必要或特許行為者不得離開家門。有一名8歲大的女孩因為沒辦法舉行生日派對，所以父母跟街坊鄰居說好，每一戶居民站在自家門前，當女孩從屋內走出家門時，合力唱起生日快樂歌，在不觸犯防疫條例的情況下，替女孩營造不一樣的生日驚喜。"},{"pid":"a5a2fdb1fdc46cf74ad4c39604188aa432618edb","tid":1954243,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T16:29:28.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/03/31/99/7672331.jpg&amp;s=Y&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=262&amp;sh=401&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=400\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F03%2F31%2F99%2F7672331.jpg%26s%3DY%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D262%26sh%3D401%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26w%3D400&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUi1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=14363677\" target=\"_blank\">https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/03/31/99/7672331.jpg&amp;s=Y&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=262&amp;sh=401&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=400</a>"},{"pid":"ccc5b3f63ab123991c8651d2ef69fd5a0eacc025","tid":1954243,"uid":302475,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T16:29:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e677c3f72667210446c923716486f7e27f814890","ti